properties.Name: PartySecurityQuestion
properties.Description: A security question and response that is used to verify the party's identity.

Columns.Name: PartyId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Party.

Columns.Name: SecurityQuestionNumber
Columns.Description: The number associated with the order in which the question is asked for the purpose of identification.

Columns.Name: PeriodStartTimestamp
Columns.Description: The period start timestamp that the party is associated with the security question.

Columns.Name: PeriodEndTimestamp
Columns.Description: The period end timestamp that the party is associated with the security question.

Columns.Name: PartySecurityQuestion
Columns.Description: The security question used to challenge the Party.

Columns.Name: PartySecurityQuestionResponse
Columns.Description: The response to the security question used to challenge the Party.

Columns.Name: PartySecurityQuestionNote
Columns.Description: A note, comment or additional information regarding the Party Security Question.
